Enum Class MapCursor.Type

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<MapCursor.Type>
org.bukkit.map.MapCursor.Type
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<MapCursor.Type>, Constable, net.kyori.adventure.key.Keyed, Keyed
Enclosing class:
MapCursor
public static enum MapCursor.Type extends Enum<MapCursor.Type> implements Keyed
Represents the standard types of map cursors. More may be made available by resource packs - the value is used by the client as an index in the file './assets/minecraft/textures/map/map_icons.png' from minecraft.jar or from a resource pack.
